content:
Deploying OmniScripts Off-Platform with OmniOut.

You can deploy OmniScripts to AEM, Heroku, and other Cloud Application Platforms to run them outside of the Salesforce platform. These platforms connect with Salesforce through Salesforce Cloud Authentication Components or via a Connected App.

Using OmniScript with Adobe Experience Manager: AEM is a web deployment option for OmniScript. It allows keeping OmniScripts in line with organization's designs and implementing custom elements and behaviors.

Deploying OmniScripts to Cloud Application Platforms: Cloud Application Platforms host OmniScripts by connecting to Salesforce as a Connected App or standalone app.

Making Attachments Available in External OmniScripts: To render attachments on an external OmniScript, follow the steps for rendering attachments.
title: Deploying OmniScripts Off-Platform with OmniOut
